gi%C3%A1-h%E1%BA%A1nh-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-L%C3%A2m-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-ZyrwxrlmYbFaBPuORlM3UQ">Tòng giá hạnh Thiếu Lâm tự - 從駕幸少林寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B5-T%E1%BA%AFc-Thi%C3%AAn/author-cFPknskEldD7UcWhT6LIfQ">Võ Tắc Thiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%93i/poem-ZJ_7rd5mjWaHlTNZm1f93g">Tống Lý Hồi - 送李回</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/V%E1%BB%87-Linh-s%C6%A1n/poem-HfZjQIUN0wd9AQDqvlekZw">Vệ Linh sơn - 衛靈山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/author-_a5NZkjlUmxBDVuBs6LQJg">Phạm Quý Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/V%C4%A9nh-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-tu%E1%BA%A7n-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-06/poem-FHpkvO3qWiTMba0Eu5Zdzw">Vĩnh Vương đông tuần ca kỳ 06 - 永王東巡歌其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
